{
  "texts": [
    "Our user-centric approach to data collection carefully considers two critical aspects: (i) the demographics and intentions of the content creators (\"Who?",
    "\"), and (ii) the intended audience for whom the content is written (\"Whom?",
    "The initial phase of our data collection methodology involved using Google Search to identify a preliminary set of websites, denoted as X = [Time for Kids, News for Kids,.",
    ", Kids Press].",
    "Subsequently, we employed ChatGPT, prompting it with \"List websites similar to X i that offer kid-specific content\", to expand our list."
  ]
}